N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 665.14 - Appeals and review

State Regulations

An appeal from, or an application for review of, any
decision, determination or order under this Part may be made to the Freshwater

Wetlands Appeals Board or to a court of competent jurisdiction pursuant to the
provisions of title 11 of the act. Notes
